							},
							"string" : "{{olObject:uid=bxa2q7p4p77y2gknwl4yuaikj}}: They are missing, but here is a brilliant workaround (via [this bugzilla issue](https://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=113772#c6)):"
						}
