							"paragraphStyle" : {
								"__type" : "textStyle"
							},
							"string" : "Can be inherited from linked projects:\n- For example, beneficiaries can be ingerited as a default, or overridden/declared locally\n- Value can be derived transitively e.g. martial arts supports fitness, education"
